data.description: Motivated Seller. None Restricted Property and Best Deal of Area! One of a kind 2story, 4bedrooms, 3 rooms down including primary, 3baths, game room and a wet bar upstairs. A beautiful house that sits over 1/2 an acre of land with mature trees in a country-like setting. This beauty is located in Pinehurst with NO HOA, low taxes. Updated kitchen cabinets, quartz countertops, LV flooring downstairs lots of storage in attic and 3y/o roof.  A dishwasher can be put in upon request as seller is currently using the area as garbage can compartment. This property has a water well for water supply so taxes are super low. Zoned to Tomball schools with nearby shopping centers, Tomball Lonestar College and Hospital. This property has endless possibilities that you could customize to your own living conditions and a lot to offer the new owner. Don't missed the chance to tour this home today! it won't last long.
